<div class='commit-subject'>renderer: fix integer overflow in create shader</div><div class='commit-msg'>As the 'pkt_length' and 'offlen' can be malicious from guest,
the vrend_create_shader function has an integer overflow, this
will make the next 'memcpy' oob access. This patch avoid this.

Signed-off-by: Li Qiang &lt;liq3ea@gmail.com&gt;
Signed-off-by: Dave Airlie &lt;airlied@redhat.com&gt;
